			<p><span lang="it" xml:lang="it">Chris Wallace   has implemented an XML page on which you can see and print the mouseover   pictures individually. <a href="http://dsa2006.blogspot.com/2007/02/periodic-table-of-visualisations.html" target="_blank">More information</a></span></p>
			<p><span lang="it" xml:lang="it">&nbsp;</span>On another page by Chris you can group the   visualization methods by your criteria and you can find background information   for a specific visualization method via 'Google Images' and 'Wikipedia'. <br />
